<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٣٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٢٧٧٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بَكْرٍ قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ فُضَيْلٍ، عَنِ النُّعْمَانِ بْنِ قَيْسٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَا اسْتَيْسَرَ مِنَ الْهَدْيِ شَاةٌ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>